tes (180°C). Cover with foil and bake for a further 25-30 minutes (180°C) until buns are puffed and golden and internal temperature reads 75°C.","Let buns rest in baking dish for 5 minutes, then carefully and quickly invert onto a large serving plate, transferring any caramel left behind to the tops and sides of the buns. Serve warm."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Dough","content":["180 g milk","80 g unsalted butter, melted and cooled, plus extra for greasing","4 egg yolks, from large eggs","1 large egg","1 Tbsp granulated sugar","2 ¼ tsp dried instant yeast","480 g plain flour, plus extra for dusting","1 tsp fine sea salt"]},{"title":"Caramel Sauce","content":["160 g unsalted butter, diced","160 g double cream","320 g dark brown sugar","1 ½ Tbsp vanilla bean paste"]},{"title":"Filling","content":["200 g pecan nuts, toasted","50 g dark brown sugar","50 g caster sugar","1 tsp ground cinnamon","1 pinch fine sea salt"]},{"title":"Assembly","content":["20 g unsalted butter, melted"]}],"id":"r265314","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-dujKFZ8QI4c\/XZWqx7UvhkI\/AAAAAAAAfdM\/kC9qwkCoGWkfP97BEWyLAkJ7OdgouZsaQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_UWClYSh74VU67U0C.png","title":"Christmas Morning Sticky Buns","publishedAt":"2017-12-18T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"9 g","fat":"41 g","uom":"per 1 piece","carbohydrates":"68 g","calories":"2851 kJ \/ 683 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large bowl, cling film, rolling pin, pastry brush, serrated knife, aluminium foil, large baking tray, temperature probe, serving plate, baking dish (32 cm x 20 cm x 5 cm), fridge, oven","hintsAndTricks":["If you would prefer to bake the buns the same day, at <nobr>step 8<\/nobr> cover with cling film and prove another <nobr>1-2 hours<\/nobr> at room temperature until buns press tightly together, then continue recipe from <nobr>step 10.<\/nobr>"],"basicInfo":["medium","15m","17h 50m","12 pieces"]}